
Overview of noun pestle

The noun pestle has 3 senses (no senses from tagged texts)
                                       
1. stamp, pestle -- (machine consisting of a heavy bar that moves vertically for pounding or crushing ores)
2. pestle, muller, pounder -- (a heavy tool of stone or iron (usually with a flat base and a handle) that is used to grind and mix material (as grain or drugs or pigments) against a slab of stone)
3. pestle -- (a club-shaped hand tool for grinding and mixing substances in a mortar)

